if; color:#656A77;''> No tenemos dudas de que eres tú. Para iniciar sesión, utiliza el siguiente código de verificación. </p> <h2 style=''margin-top:36px; font-size:18px; line-height:24px; font-weight: 700; color:#28BBC9; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; margin-bottom: 16px;''> Codigo de verificación: </h2> <p style=''color: #656A77; font-size: 24px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;''><strong style=''margin-right: 4px; background: #FFFFFF; border-radius: 4px; padding: 8px 4px 8px 12px;''>verification_code_1 </strong> <strong style=''margin-right: 4px; background: #FFFFFF; border-radius: 4px; text-align: center; padding: 8px 4px 8px 12px;''>verification_code_2 </strong> <strong style=''margin-right: 4px; background: #FFFFFF; border-radius: 4px; padding: 8px 4px 8px 12px;''>verification_code_3 </strong> <strong style=''margin-right: 4px; background: #FFFFFF; border-radius: 4px; padding: 8px 4px 8px 12px;''>verification_code_4 </strong> <strong style=''margin-right: 4px; background: #FFFFFF; border-radius: 4px; padding: 8px 8px 8px 12px;''>verification_code_5 </strong> <strong style=''background: #FFFFFF; border-radius: 4px; padding: 8px 12px 8px 12px;''>verification_code_6 </strong> </p> <p style=''height: 1px; margin-top: 24px; margin-bottom: 24px; background-color: #d1d5df;''></p></td> </tr> <tr> <td style=''padding:0; margin: 0''> <table role=''presentation'' style=''width:100%; border-collapse:collapse; border:0; border-spacing:0;''> <tr> <td><p style=''margin:0; font-size:16px; line-height:20px; color:#656A77; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; text-align: center;''> Si no fue usted, <a href=''domain/auth/forgot_password'' style=''color:#FF9E1B; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; text-decoration:none;''>cambie su contraseña</a> para proteger su cuenta. </p></td> </tr> </table> </td> </tr> </table> </td> </tr> <tr> <td style=''margin:0; padding:24px;''> <table role=''presentation'' style=''width:100%; border-collapse:collapse; border:0; border-spacing:0;''> <tr> <td><p style=''margin: 0 0 12px 0; font-size: 14px; text-align: center; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; color: #384461;''> Conectate con nosotros </p></td> </tr> <tr> <td style=''text-align: center;''><a href=''social_linkedin'' style=''text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; display: inline-block; width: 36px; height: 36px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; margin-right: 32px;''> <img src=''domain/assets/images/email/linkedin.png'' width=''36px'' height=''36px'' alt=''Linkedin'' style=''width: 36px; height: 36px;''> </a> <a href=''social_facebook'' style=''text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; display: inline-block; width: 36px; height: 36px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; margin-right: 32px;''> <img src=''domain/assets/images/email/facebook.png'' width=''36px'' height=''36px'' alt=''Facebook'' style=''width: 36px; height: 36px; display: block;''> </a> <a href=''social_instagram'' style=''text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; display: inline-block; width: 36px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; height: 36px;''> <img src=''domain/assets/images/email/instagram.png'' width=''36px'' height=''36px'' alt=''Instagram'' style=''width: 36px; height: 36px;''> </a></td> </tr> <tr> <td><p style=''margin:8px 0 8px 0; font-size:14px; line-height:16px; color:#384461; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; text-align: center;''> Por favor no responder a este correo directamente, ya que esta casilla de correo no es revisada. </p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td><p style=''margin:8px 0 8px 0; font-size:14px; line-height:16px; color:#384461; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; text-align: center;''> &copy; current_year <a href=''web_site'' style=''color:#FF9E1B; text-decoration:none;''>WORLD POS SOLUTIONS</a> - Todos los derechos reservados </p></td> </tr> <tr> <td><p style=''margin:8px 0 8px 0; font-size:14px; line-height:16px; color:#384461; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; text-align: center;''> Colombia </p></td> </tr> </table> </td> </tr> </table> </td> </tr> </table> </body> </html> ');

