ng'' width=''36px'' height=''36px'' alt=''Linkedin'' style=''width: 36px; height: 36px;''> </a> <a href=''social_facebook'' style=''text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; display: inline-block; width: 36px; height: 36px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; margin-right: 32px;''> <img src=''domain/assets/images/email/facebook.png'' width=''36px'' height=''36px'' alt=''Facebook'' style=''width: 36px; height: 36px; display: block;''> </a> <a href=''social_instagram'' style=''text-decoration: none; cursor: pointer; display: inline-block; width: 36px; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; height: 36px;''> <img src=''domain/assets/images/email/instagram.png'' width=''36px'' height=''36px'' alt=''Instagram'' style=''width: 36px; height: 36px;''> </a></td> </tr> <tr> <td><p style=''margin:8px 0 8px 0; font-size:14px; line-height:16px; color:#384461; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; text-align: center;''> Por favor no responder a este correo directamente, ya que esta casilla de correo no es revisada. </p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td><p style=''margin:8px 0 8px 0; font-size:14px; line-height:16px; color:#384461; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; text-align: center;''> &copy; current_year <a href=''web_site'' style=''color:#FF9E1B; text-decoration:none;''>WORLD POS SOLUTIONS</a> - Todos los derechos reservados </p></td> </tr> <tr> <td><p style=''margin:8px 0 8px 0; font-size:14px; line-height:16px; color:#384461; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; text-align: center;''> Colombia </p></td> </tr> </table> </td> </tr> </table> </td> </tr> </table> </body> </html> ');

